text: The Delhi women's cricket team is an Indian domestic cricket team based in Delhi. The team has represented the state in Senior women’s one day league (List A) and Senior women's T20 league. ==Curren Players== *Latika Kumari *Reema Malhotra *Soni Yadav *Babita Negi *Priya Punia *Shilpa Gupta *Anushka Sharma *Sonam Kapoor ==References== Category:Cricket in Delhi Category:Women's cricket teams in India
title: Delhi women's cricket team
